</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65023249"><p>About 3 years ago, they imposed a rule that would forbid English tutoring by foreign teachers online. They said that the expectations for kids getting into better schools were getting so difficult that it was causing families to not be able to afford having multiple kids. So, the government just made the blanket statement that forbid that tutoring, so they could say, "There! Now, education is cheaper! We fixed the problem!"</p></div>
	</div>

